def updaterecord(request, id):
  plat = request.POST['platera']
  kop = request.POST['kopurua']
  member = Platera.objects.get(id=id)
  member.platera = plat
  member.kopurua = kop
  member.save()
  return HttpResponseRedirect(reverse('index'))
